LEGAL INFORMATION
Center Parcs Europe B.V. is the agent for all Center Parcs villages in the Netherlands, Belgium, France and Germany (*). In this capacity Center Parcs Europe B.V. is the party to approach for bookings, booking enquiries, website queries and more.
The contact details are as follows:
Rivium Boulevard 213
2909 LK Capelle aan den IJssel
The Netherlands
Phone: +31 10 498 97 54
Correspondence address:
Center Parcs Europe B.V.
PO Box 5052
2900 EB Capelle aan den IJssel (the Netherlands)
* Excluding Park Sandur. Parc Sandur (Sunparks B.V. Rivium Boulevard 213, 2909LK Capelle aan den IJssel, Chamber of Commerce no. 24413534, VAT no. NL 817870702B01) is the party to approach for bookings, booking enquiries, website queries and more. The above contact details can also be used for this purpose. Sunparks B.V. is also the party with whom an agreement is entered when making bookings for Parc Sandur.
When a booking is made, an agreement is created between you and the entity that operates on behalf of the village where you book. No agreement is entered into between you and Center Parcs Europe B.V.
